fuzzytime 0.6 (2011.01.21)
A clock and timer that tell the time in a more familiar way (the 'ten past six'-style)


DEPENDENCIES:
– The Glasgow Haskell Compiler (http://www.haskell.org/ghc/)
– CmdArgs (http://community.haskell.org/~ndm/cmdargs/)


INSTALL:
runhaskell Setup.hs configure --prefix=/usr --docdir=/usr/share/doc/$pkgname -O
runhaskell Setup.hs build
runhaskell Setup.hs install
